room_title: Escape room "Pharaoh's Tomb" by Solve The Room in Toms River
room_description: ‘I’ve found it! The tomb of Pharaoh Nebka! I’m going in.’ That was the last you heard from your friend. Is it true then? The story of the Mummy’s Curse? Being an explorer like him, you resolve to enter the tomb yourself and find out what happened to him….
